PUT {{LightsAPIHost}}/lights/9/dimTo/40
###
PUT {{LightsAPIHost}}/lights/10/dimTo/25
###
PUT {{LightsAPIHost}}/lights/10/dimTo/100
###
# Switch off the lights
PUT {{LightsAPIHost}}/lights/9/switch/false
###
PUT {{LightsAPIHost}}/lights/10/switch/false
###
